OL,6,FIts report on the issue argued that,
OL,7,Fahead of a general election, this was
OL,8,Fa time for all political parties to
OL,9,F"make meaningful commitments on this
OL,10,Fimportant children's rights issue".
OL,12,FProfessor Andrew Rowland, a consultant
OL,13,Fpaediatrician and RCPCH officer for
OL,14,Fchild protection, said physical
OL,15,Fpunishment could also result in a
OL,16,Fchild having the learned belief that
OL,17,Fviolence was accepted and this could
OL,18,F"lead to further instances of violence
OL,19,Fand harm later in life".
