OL,6,F"The laws around physical punishment
OL,7,Fas they stand are unjust and
OL,8,Fdangerously vague," Prof Rowland said.
OL,10,F"They create a grey area in which some
OL,11,Fforms of physical punishment may be
OL,12,Flawful, and some are not."
