OL,6,FHe said society's views on punishment
OL,7,Fhad changed over time, with a majority
OL,8,Fof adults agreeing that physical
OL,9,Fpunishment of children was
OL,10,Funacceptable.
OL,12,FProf Rowland said: "There must be no
OL,13,Fgrey areas when it comes to
OL,14,Fsafeguarding children. Changing the
OL,15,Flaws in England and Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fwill give us absolute clarity and
OL,17,Fensure there are no instances where it
OL,18,Fis acceptable or lawful to smack a
OL,19,Fchild."
